rows.label: qst200310_msg0003
rows.name:
It grabbed me suddenly and took me
to the roof! The brute!

rows.label: qst200310_msg0004
rows.name: I thought it would be the end of me!

rows.label: qst200310_msg0005
rows.name:
It didn't really hurt me though,
but still...

rows.label: qst200310_msg0006
rows.name:
You know, you'd have thought someone
would have got injured, what with all
the commotion it caused.

rows.label: qst200310_msg0007
rows.name:
Even the building avoided
any major damage.

rows.label: qst200310_msg0009
rows.name:
Anyway! However you look at it,
I hope someone chases the monster
away, and soon!
